data.title: TEENAGE MUTANT NINJA TURTLES FILMS|TV SERIES (1987-2016)
data.meta_description: The Original Films|Animated Tv Series & Remakes
data.text:
Four teenage mutant ninja turtles emerge from the shadows to protect New York City from a gang of criminal ninjas.

The Turtles discover their origins while they endeavour to save New York City from the evil Shredder and his Foot Clan.

When journalist April O'Neil discovers an ancient scepter with magical powers, the Turtles must cow-a-bunga their way back to 17th century Japan to rescue her from the evil clutches of Lord Norinaga.

When the world is threatened by an ancient evil, the Ninja Turtles must reunite and overcome their faults in order to stand against it.

When a kingpin threatens New York City, a group of mutated turtle warriors must emerge from the shadows to protect their home.

The Turtles get into another battle with their enemy the Shredder, who has acquired new allies: the mutant thugs Bebop and Rocksteady and the alien being Krang.

The pizza-loving, shell-busting mutant turtles Leonardo, Donatello, Raphael and Michelangelo, with the guidance of their Sensei Master Splinter, face fierce enemies, save humanity from extinction and battle against life-altering mutations.
